title: Fowles, Lynx Even WNBA Finals with Win
text:
Fowles, Lynx Even WNBA Finals with Win 
By Zach Schneider Fowles, Lynx Even WNBA Finals with Win October 6, 2015 Updated Oct 6, 2015 at 9:59 PM CDT 
Minneapolis, MN (NNCNOW.com) --- Sylvia Fowles finished with a team-high 21 points and nine rebounds on Tuesday night as she and the Minnesota Lynx beat the Indiana Fever 77-71 to even the WNBA Finals at a game apiece. 
Maya Moore added 19 points in the winning effort, and Seimone Augustus was also in double digits with 11.
